    <anchor n="T.50.2061.0765c05"/><head><date from-iso="0618-06-21" key="j19469512052491" to-iso="0907-06-06">唐</date><placeName key="PL000000023659">洛京龍興寺</placeName><persName key="A010332">崇珪</persName>傳（<persName key="A010334">全植</persName>）</head><p><lb
ed="T" n="0765c06"/><persName key="A010332">釋崇珪</persName>，姓姜氏，<placeName key="PL000000023997">郟城</placeName>人也。門傳儒素，相綴<lb
ed="T" n="0765c07"/>簪裾。自<date from-iso="0742" key="j19921141997410" to-iso="0756">天寶</date>已來，<persName key="A008454">安</persName><persName key="A010333">史</persName>之亂，侵敗王略，家<lb
ed="T" n="0765c08"/>族遷蕩。父為商賈趨利。遵塗於<placeName key="PL000000023129">鞏</placeName><placeName key="PL000000023581">洛</placeName>間。父<lb
ed="T" n="0765c09"/>亡于逆旅，<persName key="A010332">珪</persName>慨責曰：「少遭不造，孑遺哀煢！」<lb
ed="T" n="0765c10"/>遂議出家。至<date key="j20033932003757" from-iso="0773-01-01" to-iso="0773-12-31">年十八</date>，經業蔚通得度。俄有<lb
ed="T" n="0765c11"/>雲水之興，遊<placeName key="PL000000028928">南嶽</placeName>。棲息數齡起迴，樂<placeName key="PL000000011072">南徐<lb
ed="T" n="0765c12"/>茅山</placeName>，乃依<placeName key="PL000000009026">棲霞寺</placeName>。<persName key="A010332">珪</persName>已登徑門，道聲洋溢。<lb
ed="T" n="0765c13"/>會<placeName key="PL000000000962">贊皇</placeName><persName key="A009040">李公德裕</persName>廉問是邦，延諸<placeName key="PL000000042330">慈和寺</placeName>。一<lb
ed="T" n="0765c14"/>交雅談，如遊形器之外，曰：「<ref type="person" target="#A010332">吾</ref>有幽憂之疾，<lb
ed="T" n="0765c15"/>非是居侯藩聚落之人也。」明歲遂行，重抵<lb
ed="T" n="0765c16"/><placeName key="PL000000023255">嵩少</placeName>，居于嶽寺。<date from-iso="0828-01-25" key="j20235052023888" to-iso="0829-02-11"><app type="multiplier" xml:id="begd1e15421"/>太<anchor xml:id="endd1e15421"/>和戊申歲</date>，<placeName key="PL000000023581">洛下</placeName>亢陽，唯<lb
ed="T" n="0765c17"/><ref type="place" target="#PL000000023253">嶽</ref>中雨信相繼。或謂為<persName key="A010332">珪</persName>之德動龍神之故<lb
ed="T" n="0765c18"/>也。<date from-iso="0836-01-26" key="j20264282026811" to-iso="0837-02-12">開成元年</date>，<persName key="A009040">贊皇公</persName>攝塚宰，請<persName key="A010332">珪</persName>於<placeName key="PL000000023659">洛龍<lb
ed="T" n="0765c19"/>興寺</placeName>化徒。<ref type="place" target="#PL000000042189 #PL000000023581">兩京</ref>緇白往來問道，檀施交駢。<lb
ed="T" n="0765c20"/>其所談法，宗<persName key="A009582">秀</persName>之提唱，獲益明心者多矣。<lb
ed="T" n="0765c21"/>忽告眾決別，入方丈而滅，春秋八十六。<ref type="person" target="#A004029">白<lb
ed="T" n="0765c22"/>侍郎</ref>撰《塔銘》。<date key="j20284742028474" when-iso="0841-09-02">會昌元年辛酉八月十日</date>入塔<lb
ed="T" n="0765c23"/>云。次<placeName key="PL000000010610">淮南都梁山</placeName><persName key="A010334">釋全植</persName>，姓芮，<placeName key="PL000000025908">光州</placeName>人也。少<lb
ed="T" n="0765c24"/>稟異操，自言學作佛度生去。忽投本州<placeName key="PL000000025892">榮<lb
ed="T" n="0765c25"/>光禪院</placeName><persName key="A010340">大智</persName>下求度。<ref type="person" target="#A010334">師</ref>頗嚴謹，約其誦經。<lb
ed="T" n="0765c26"/>受具後，至<placeName key="PL000000023581">洛陽</placeName>，參問禪法，徹了無疑辭。<persName key="A010334">師</persName><lb
ed="T" n="0765c27"/>觀方至<placeName key="PL000000010610">淮南都梁山</placeName>，建立茅舍。太守<persName key="A010341">衛文<lb
ed="T" n="0765c28"/>卿</persName>命於州治<placeName key="PL000000023652">長壽寺</placeName>化徒。<persName key="A010341">衛侯</persName>問：「將來佛<lb
ed="T" n="0765c29"/>法隆替若何？」<persName key="A010334">植</persName>曰：「真實之物無振，自古于<pb ed="T" n="0766a" xml:id="T50.2061.0766a"/><lb
ed="T" n="0766a01"/>今，往復軌躅。有為之法，四相遷流。法當陻<lb
ed="T" n="0766a02"/>厄。<ref type="person" target="#A010341">君侯</ref>翹足可見。」預言<persName key="A006570">武宗</persName>毀教也。<persName key="A010334">植</persName>終<lb
ed="T" n="0766a03"/>年九十三，門人建塔立碑。<date key="j20296242029624" when-iso="0844-10-26">會昌四年甲子九<lb
ed="T" n="0766a04"/>月七日</date>入浮圖焉。</p>
